last night’s golden globes ended not with a bang but with a whimper. or, at least, a baffling decision. bohemian rhapsody, the weakest of the five nominees in the best motion picture – drama category, defied the bookies’ odds and won the biggest award of the evening.

though it was a box-office smash, the film, which stars rami malek as queen frontman freddie mercury, has been accused of mishandling the late singer’s sexuality. a review in forbes magazine accused it of “refram[ing] his life story as an afterschool special about the dangers of partying and gay sex ... whether it’s homophobic or old-school slut-shaming, it’s icky”. the decision to hire director bryan singer, who has faced numerous sexual assault accusations dating back to the nineties (allegations he denies), also caused consternation.

on quality alone, the film didn’t deserve to beat four such powerful, confidently realised creations as black panther, blackkklansman, if beale street could talk and a star is born. but given the more troubling context around it, bohemian rhapsody‘s win felt even more jarring – particularly on a night that celebrated change and progress in the wake of the solemn mood that (rightly) defined last year’s proceedings.

in 2018, after a litany of film industry men were accused of grossly abusing their power, largely triggered by the sexual assault allegations against hollywood heavyweight harvey weinstein, the golden globes were a sombre affair. with time’s up and #metoo movements gathering steam, actresses wore black on the red carpet, brought activists as their dates, and donned time’s up pins: a far cry from the usual, “who are you wearing?” awards ceremony frivolity.

the need for change had become impossible to ignore, and the night was dominated by a palpable, necessary tension. full credit @the.independent #goldenglobes #goldenglobe #film #tv #netflix #filmnews #actors #awards #goldenglobeawards

text:
2018 marked the one-year anniversary of the #metoo movement, and while uk businesses, charities and politics continue to be hit by scandal and allegations of misconduct, the latter part of 2018 has seen a shift from outrage to action.
nonetheless, while the #metoo movement has been empowering, there are rumblings that it may also be a poison chalice. bloomberg reported a particularly worrying response of wall street firms to the movement whereby male colleagues are now reluctant to dine or travel with their female counterparts, while others prefer not to put themselves in one-on-one situations with female colleagues such as meetings, reviews or mentoring. in light of this, would it be too extreme to suggest that men may be more reluctant to hire women?
 so how do we tackle these attitudes? how do we ensure the issue of workplace harassment is taken seriously and addressed effectively without having a negative impact on diversity?
the key here is to involve men in the conversation. female only panel discussions attended by female only audiences are not environments for change. indeed, a comsres survey in 2017 found that 18% of men had experienced unwanted sexual behaviour in the workplace so this isn’t exclusively a “woman’s issue”.
we need to avoid further polarising gender issues and discuss the challenges collectively – as i’ve said before, men are allies, not enemies.

text:
שקד קמחי סטודנטית בשנה ב׳ לתקש״ח בשנקר יצרה סדרת חולצות מחפיצות כחלק מקורס העברת מסר בהנחיית יעל בוגן.
.
👔👚👕
.
״חולצה מחפיצה נוצרה כחלק מפרויקט ללימודים בשנקר, והיא מורכבת מעיקרון פשוט - משפטים שנאמרים לנשים מודפסים ונלבשים על ידן.  בהרבה מקרים קל להוציא מילים מהפה, וקשה לראות מישהי הולכת איתן, ועל קו התפר הזה הפרויקט מתפקד. המשפטים המודפסים מאוד מגוונים - החל ממשפטי פתיחה קלילים ומוכרים ועד ביטויים קשים לקריאה, וזאת על מנת לעורר שיח על השפה שבה אנו משתמשים.
כל הרווחים ממכירת החולצות עוברים כתרומה לארגונים חברתיים משתנים, בימים אלה כל הרווחים הם תרומה לאיגוד מרכזי הסיוע לנפגעות ונפגעי תקיפה מינית בישראל״.
.
פרויקט אקטואלי, רלוונטי, רגיש ומתוחכם !🌸
.
מוזמנים/ות לבקר בעמוד הפייסבוק חולצה מחפיצה של שקד ואף לרכוש לכם/ן חולצה מחפיצה משלכם/ן!
🦖
https://www.facebook.com/hultza.mach/
.
@shakedkimhi @visual_shenkar @shenkar_college

text:
hey fam. we need to have a conversation. i'll be moderating this dialogue. i hope you'll join us.
.
in the aftermath of the #rkelly documentary, we invite you to join us for a live facebook roundtable discussion: how can we stop failing black women and girls?

wednesday, january 9th at 9pm est.

we will be joined by christopher everage edgar-smith, llmsw, clinical therapist specializing in addiction treatment with a trauma-focused lense. "if there's one thing these six hours have taught us, it's that culturally we have failed black women and girls."- @thegrio.
.

text:
ladies imagine this:

we stop idealizing marriage and start acting like a (insert age) year old with her whole life ahead of her.  you go to that dream school, you get an education, you travel the world, you write that book,  you start a business and you stop assuming your life starts and ends witb a husband. .
.
.
i chose this picture because i once drank the koolaid.  i once thought my only puropse was to nurture those around me.  i married young and poured myself into his dreams and the dreams of being married and raising beautiful, self assured children.  i left myself and my dreams on the back burner so much that it took  years to figure out which dreams were my own.
.
.
.
this is a picture of a trip i paid for.  that i took my children on.  a hike deep in the  jungle that i wanted to take.  where we found a waterfall (a huge passion of mine) that i wanted to swim in.  i got out of my own way during this trip.  i set my own fears aside.  i nurtured my dreams (and my children too)!! turns out both can happen at once!! ladies please love yourselves.  you are an entity worthy of love and compassion and you deserve to be a priority!!!
#loribrinkleycounseling #mentalwellness #boundaries #selfloverevolution #metoo

text:
i've watched the qspiracy since the beginning.

steve bannon left the wh august 2017 and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences? 'j-c' church militant, anyone?

abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit a hijacked party is just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt, with the goonsquad known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this and messes with the boombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on me me me bed. obviously someone has a lot to lose when none of the us intelligence agencies ends this loonatic travesty.

qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that goebbels would have died for. it is clear that stuff like pizzagate™ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still.

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are useless with the content - no way they are going to risk their business by taking responsibility.

there is no way that gop isn't aware of this - after all, cambridge analytica worked for ted cruz and john bolton. the whole narrative is built on the same facebook user data that bannon and the mercers reportedly got as cambridge analytica. pedofiles - i bet - but the way things are bundled sure makes goebbels shiver.

trump plays along with his tweets, gestures and words. the bigger issue still - the republicans willingly piggybacked this before the midterms and still keep abusing the faith of their fellow men.

this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

text:
it took me some time to watch this on @lifetimetv. mostly because i was a victim of sexual abuse by multiple predators and starting when i was only 6 years old. there are monsters out there and some of them are even in your family. there will always be trauma. you can’t get back what has been taken and it hurts to see these women relive those moments by telling the world. it would hurt even more if nothing is done.  #metoo *** this is also why you always see me with my children because i’m paranoid. anytime i left them with a sitter i would give them full body checks and also would ask them how their day was, look them in the eyes when they speak. listen to their voice and watch for anything that was alarming including sudden change in behavior. it’s getting harder with social events like play dates and drop off birthday parties but i also rely on my parenting skills and raise my kids to also be alert. no going off alone or playing “touch” with anyone. you have your bubble stay in it and make sure you don’t invade anyone else’s. 
this is my life now and i try to not be too overbearing and i don’t want to cause anxiety in my children so when they ask too many “whys” i just say because i’m mom. periodt. #lifeofasurvivor

text:
i've watched the qspiracy since the beginning.

steve bannon left the wh august 2017 and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences? 'j-c' church militant, anyone?

abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit a hijacked party is just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt, with the goonsquad known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this and messes with the boombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on me me me bed. obviously someone has a lot to lose when none of the us intelligence agencies ends this loonatic travesty.

qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that goebbels would have died for. it is clear that stuff like pizzagate™ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still.

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are useless with the content - no way they are going to risk their business by taking responsibility.

there is no way that gop isn't aware of this - after all, cambridge analytica worked for ted cruz and john bolton. the whole narrative is built on the same facebook user data that bannon and the mercers reportedly got as cambridge analytica. pedofiles - i bet - but the way things are bundled sure makes goebbels shiver.

trump plays along with his tweets, gestures and words. the bigger issue still - the republicans willingly piggybacked this before the midterms and still keep abusing the faith of their fellow men.

this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

text:
showing no sign of abating, the #metoo movement continued to traverse the globe in full force. morphing under new names from #anakaman in egypt to #sendearlat in turkey, #beknownbeheard in nigeria. 
the conversation on sexual abuse grew and the can of worms began to open on sexual offenders across the world, unseating powerful men in it's path from politics to entertainment. 
the pressure increased on the government and companies alike to change their polices on violence against women. 
#metoo in u.s. alone cost more than 200 prominent men their jobs. the u.s. equal employment opportunity commission recovered nearly usd 70 million on behalf of sexual harassment survivors in 2018 fiscal year. 
sadly africa, (nigeria especially) is far behind in the fight against gender-based violence and other offenses of sexual nature.. at truss we have highlighted a numbers of activities for 2019 which includes partnerships to continually join forces with other organizations at the fore front of this fight with the aim of propelling nigeria towards the sdgs and getting a 50/50  world where men and women have equal opportunities by #2030

we are excited about all the work we are set to do to empower women across board.. we can't wait to tell all women #workitmama .
.
.
#trussempowermentfoundation
#beknownbeheard

i've watched the qspiracy since the beginning.

steve bannon left the wh august 2017 and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences? 'j-c' church militant, anyone?

abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit a hijacked party is just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt, with the goonsquad known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this and messes with the boombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on me me me bed. obviously someone has a lot to lose when none of the us intelligence agencies ends this loonatic travesty.

qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that goebbels would have died for. it is clear that stuff like pizzagate™ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still.

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are useless with the content - no way they are going to risk their business by taking responsibility.

there is no way that gop isn't aware of this - after all, cambridge analytica worked for ted cruz and john bolton. the whole narrative is built on the same facebook user data that bannon and the mercers reportedly got as cambridge analytica. pedofiles - i bet - but the way things are bundled sure makes goebbels shiver.

trump plays along with his tweets, gestures and words. the bigger issue still - the republicans willingly piggybacked this before the midterms and still keep abusing the faith of their fellow men.

this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

text:
there are so many hurting people out here hurting other people. 
it's not any one person's fault, but it does require that we each acknowledge and accept what is being shared/expressed.

#muterkelly and #metoo go hand in hand with #saysomething and #tellsomebody.

parents, please listen to your children and watch for physical queues. if you don't speak up and protect them,  you leave them to hurt all through life and wait for that pain to manifest in other,seemingly odd, ways or times.

victims and survivors, please be alright with growing through your trauma. don't allow anyone to diminish your experiences just so they can feel like they're helping you. be strong in acknowledging and accepting that you were wronged and victimized by someone.

stop trying to make healing and forgiveness happen overnight. yes...you are better than you were yesterday. but,  all the things you had to face, feel and fight through as a victim are what made/ makes/ will make you victorious.

text:
a few years ago i made the biggest change ever in my life by deciding to break free from a toxic relationship that was killing me physically, mentally, emotionally, and spiritually. since then,  i've had to adjust and survive as a single mother of three along with juggling day to day obstacles. but, i learned how to make it work and have been living a happier and healthier life since. now, i'm no stranger to overcoming challenges and leaving a toxic relationship was just one of the many struggles i've had to overcome. ***
join on january 16 @ 7pm est for my free webinar (linktree in bio to sign up) where we will discuss the tools and resources i used to walk away from a toxic relationship, become a published author, and begin the journey to creating the life i always wanted. the first five people to sign up will receive a free copy of my book let mia tell it and everyone will receive my 30 day breaking toxic cycles journal for free! ***

text:
here is an article about dry january and how it's not so bad but i thought this was the most interesting line.... it's so challenging to be sober even for someone without a drinking problem that he lies about it because it is that bad to deal with the comments this decision comes with. 
this man doesn't want to deal with the judgemental looks and mean comments so he just lies but i refuse to lie about consuming alcohol. why should i have to? why is soberity so scandalous?

when i first got sober one of my "friends" told me to lie about this, no man would ever date me if i had a drinking problem.  it's so sad that this is somewhat true and that we are in a society where sobriety is so shocking is must be kept secret. 
there are 15 million people who are struggling with alcohol addiction and as a society we have been so rude and mean about sobriety that these people feel it's best to lie about it, there is no way they will be accepted as they are. to think my friends are dying from alcohol abuse and they can't tell anyone, what other illness is treated without any compassion and must be lied about? why? why do we treat alcoholic people so badly? we glamorize the recovery of celebrities like rob lowe but not our friends and family members. 
let's end the stigma attached to sobriety 
let's stop lying about how wonderful alcohol is and be more accepting of someone's decision to say no thanks 
#drydiet #sober #nohangover #noalcohol #metoo #transformation #soberissexy #soberyogi #transformation #liveyourtruth #soberaf #recovery #recoveroutloud

text: #абьюз я хотела написать этот пост, когда все закончится окончательно. но события в моей жизни происходят все чудесатее и чудесатее и конца этому не видно. хотелось бы сказать, что виной этому мой муж, но нет, виной этому-я, отсутствие у меня личных границ и тотальная неуверенность в себе. бежать надо было изначально, когда я сразу же не понравилась его семье, и от него не было попыток как-то нас «помирить», но на какой хер я вцепилась в это, я до сих пор не понимаю. потом вроде все было нормально, но, взятая ипотека достаточно быстро показала его истинное лицо. у меня тупая работа с маленькой зп, я сама тупая долбоебка, у меня нет друзей и родители мои деревенские чмо! а еще я плавать не умею и английский не знаю, в голове только косметика🤷🏼‍♀️вот вы бы женились на таком человеке? а мне вот повезло, и на мне такой женились🤣теперь не знаю, как от этого избавиться-то, пока что я только в минусе, и морально, и материально, а он живет и радуется жизни! в общем, мораль каждый найдет свою, а у меня один совет, к которому я никогда в жизни не прислушивалась, слушайте себя и свое сердце, оно никогда не подведет. ну и поставьте за меня свечку, что ли, а то как справляться со всем этим всем, я уже хз🙏🏻🤦🏼‍♀️ #деструктивныеотношения #абьюзер #abuse #янебоюсьсказать #metoo

text:
day 6 & 7 • red january ❤️
•
•
i had some trouble uploading yesterday so i've put these days together in one post ☺️.
•
•
i'm still really sick which is making @redjanuaryuk really hard at the moment. for now i'm sticking with yoga until i'm well enough to do some more intense exercises outside. 🧘 •
•
for the past couple of days i have been thinking about what i want to achieve this year. i've been very open about my mental health issues, but also, in a way, feel like i sugar coat it a lot. i try very hard to be positive and to be a friend to those that struggle too. however, i feel like i need to be more honest about my c-ptsd and my experience as a sexual abuse survivor. to put it lightly.. this shit isn't easy, and i'm becoming more aware of how strongly ptsd effects my everyday life. i'm ready to be more open and unapologetically honest. who's with me? 💪🌷

text:
i’ll just say this… the people that work for #america can go longer without "a wall” — than they can without paychecks.
the #trumpshutdown will start to become really real this week — this is the story to watch — how much pressure can our 'memer-in-chief' withstand? or is #trump too far off in his own reality to do something to end the needless pain he’s inflicting  on so many everyday #americans — and our country?
why is our government shutdown over american taxpayers paying for the wall — when #mexico is supposed to be paying for the wall? 
i don't give a crap about his fan’s spins and interpretations of what he meant to say, or what he really means… he said:
"i will build a great wall -- and nobody builds walls better than me, believe me --and i'll build them very inexpensively. i will build a great, great wall on our southern border, and i will make mexico pay for that wall. mark my words."
words… marked.
he was very clear and specific. 
he wants money for his stupid wall?… it's going to have to be in pesos… 
end of discussion.
the #democrats now have control of the house and will put forth sensible legislation to benefit the people of this country. and, for the first time, hold #trump to account… his life will now become a virtual and perpetual deep colonoscopy… 
the saudis. abuse of power. corruption. ethics. kavanaugh. tax returns. #russia. obstruction of justice! you name it… we'll really start getting to the bottom of it…all! 
to save #america we must hold to account the inept, corrupt and amoral unindicted co-conspirator in the oval office: #illegitimate #failingpresident #donaldtrump.

.
.
.
.

.

.

text:
i don't believe that every abusive person is capable of murder.  i know not every survivor has a fear of being murdered...but some of us do and that fear is a tough one to shake.  when we went to mediation last year, the mediator came into the room with my attorney and me and told me kyles response to a basic question was one he had never heard before.  it was quite alarming. he then asked me what joint custody meant to me, i said "we both have a say on major life decisions; school, religion, medical" which is the obvious answer. 
kyles response "i get them when something happens to her" 
what????? first i'm not planning on going anywhere and for that to be his only reason for wanting joint custody only added to my fear of him eventually murdering me.  we have court a week from today and i know it's not going to be a good day for him. he spent the $4000 in child support and hasn't seen the boys since april.  i tried to tell the judge so many times he was only doing all of this to get back at me, he told me that, but she said i couldn't say that because he's stating he loves the boys and truly wants a relationship with them.  now, everything i said is going to be clear as day to her; his games will be seen and a narcissist never likes that.  i'm praying hard this week for safety, peace, and to keep my heart kind. 
i won't be a dateline story
(he didn't get joint custody or any set visitation) 
#building2rebuild 💜
.
.
.  #farmish #plainjane #wwhl #domesticabuse #abusedidntwin #lovelysquares #inspiremyinstagram #visualcrush #theeverygirl #oneofthebunch #feelfreefeed #morningslikethese #seekthesimplicity #darlingmovement #postitfortheaesthetic #pursuewhatislovely #bloggers #liveunscripted #domesticviolencesurvivor #metoo #christianblogger #ikeadecor #homedepotlife #lowes  #stepupyourgame  #bravotv

text:
we have all had to go through some things in order to be who we are. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
there maybe dents, scratches, scars all at various stages of healing but if you continue to go through the process of getting through it can be one of your greatest accomplishments. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
your trails and tribulations are investments in your future self. you may end up being the one to solve the problem for others you have currently. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
may the pain your endure today shine a light that leads you to the pathway of your purpose and lead to others by way of service with the gifts they give birth to. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
we are all bigger than our current (trauma) circumstances… ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
i hope you never forget that. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
find your happy⁣⁣
⁣⁣

text:
for far too long black women were seen as less than human in the sense we are expected to endure so much without breaking, we are to accept the hand we’re dealt without question. studies have shown that even in the medical profession black women are believed to be able to endure more pain and are dismissed when they come with concerns. as a result black girls are dismissed, are often taught to suppress their emotions further damaging (intentional or not) their feelings of self worth and confidence. it’s time we stop silencing our girls. their pain is real whether you agree or not. it deserves validation. give them a voice and be a part of the solution.
#traumatherapist#dvspecialist#survivor#metoo
#optimumpurpose#melanin4therapy#blackgirlsmatter
#healing#love#support#advocacy#ittakesavillage

text:
shipping art from my for there she was and #metoo series to @procreateproject for the 2019 artrooms artfair. the mother house studios organized by procreate project is the official charity project for this year's fair and as a result, they will a whole room dedicated to their artists. (way to go @dygravina and @paolettalondon !!!) the fair @artroomsfairs is this weekend janurary 11-13 in london at meliã white house, next to the south east of the regent's park. check out the link in my bio for times and how to get tickets. please go see my artwork and the work of all the other procreate project's artists. .
.
i've mentioned this project here before but in case you missed it. procreate project recently received a £22.500 pledge from the mayor of london and wrapped up a fundraising campaign to build an art studio space with childcare in london for 18-22 artists. this project is solving one of the reasons why "there are no great women artist" (l. nochlin) by providing space to work and affordable childcare to women artists. oh, yes. it is such a brilliant project. .
.
go this weekend, support this group, and buy art! #motherartist #womenartists #procreateproject #motherartprize #womeninthearts #artandmotherhood #womensupportingwomen

text:
under the control of her abuser
when he call she comes running!
he black her eye she ask why? 
he beats her senseless
she looks at him in bewilderment!
surprised every time!
she tries and she tries to be what he desires
never quite reaching the mark 
never quite being good enough
his rejection leaves her starving for his affection
trading her dignity for his acceptance!
more submissive less attractive, more agreeable less vocal, more domesticated less social, more teachable less successful! 
every time she reaches the line he moves it! 
forever chasing his delusions... just like an abused woman! 
mind control...history repeats
we keep doing the same ol' thing
and excepting something different.
insanity...
conforming to a world you weren't created to be a part of
fighting to be a part of a system perverse and corrupt
pleading, begging, marching, protesting
picket lines, picket signs
singing, screaming... #nojusticenopeace equality
generation after generation, decade after decade, year after year for hundreds of years
day after day we kneel in rejection 
beggin
cries fall on deaf ears 
if it ain't broke why fix it?
there ain't no problem if i don't see it
justice is blind! 
but we keep on tryin'
we knockin'
we dyin'
we hopin' that one day 
we'll be seen as more than three fifths of a human being! *the abuser never thinks he's abusive! *freedom's on the other side... open the door walk through it!
come up hear and see!
if we change the way we think, we'll change what we've been seeing! 
wake up
#repentorperish
 scream shout yell it out!
#4cryinoutloud911.com

stand together
#nofear
#survivors

text_retweet:
i'm not sure how many have watched the disturbing #survivingrkelly series on @lifetimetv but i watched the first 2 parts of it with my daughter. i must say, i'm all over the place with my feelings on this subject. i have so many questions. questions for the people around r. kelly, questions for the girls, questions for his family, but mainly questions for the parents who allow their minor children to hang out with and befriend adults nearly twice their age 😡😤. i don't want to hear about parents not always knowing what their children are doing. there was a pattern and these girls were with him all of the time. call me a helicopter mom, but i know who my children are with, the parents names, their addresses, how many additional adults live in the household, ect. you're not going to tell me that a 20 something year old man has 15 year old female friends. nope, nope, nope. not buying it 🙅🏾‍♀️! we all as a society have failed these girls. everyone that watched his sex tape that was released early 2002, is responsible for what happened to all those girls that followed. why didn't anyone speak up? his team, the record executives, his teachers, the parents of these girls? why are we still justifying sexual abuse by saying things like, "well why did they wait so long to talk?", or, "if it really happened he would be in jail". this way of thinking is why so many do not speak up. stop saying things like that to people! stop saying things like that out loud! i'm sure i'll have more to say on this topic in the coming days after i watch the final parts to this. if you watch it, i suggest breaking it up, it's too much to take in all in one sitting. if you've watched it, i'd love to hear your thoughts. .

"the legendary cbs news producer susan zirinsky will replace david rhodes as the president of cbs news in march, the network announced sunday evening.

cbs news chief david rhodes' decision to step down follows a tenure of great change and great turmoil, marked by shifts in personnel and formats, along with bumpy ratings, and searing scandal. text:
happy monday, y’all!! 💫⁣
⁣
you wanna know what’s so incredible?!?⁣
⁣
finally being confident in my true self and the woman i’m becoming more and more everyday.⁣
⁣
not reacting to the humans that used to trigger me with their rudeness or negativity. ⁣
⁣
living 99.9999% of my days in a state of love now. ⁣
⁣
clearing out old baggage with ease and grace on the reg. ⁣
⁣
learning my soul’s purpose a little more each day and the excitement that comes with that. ⁣
⁣
having my mind blown daily with the amount of gratitude flowing through me. ⁣
⁣
the list of awesomeness could go on and on. ⁣
⁣
the life i’ve created and will continue to intentionally create is one of magical proportions. ⁣
⁣
life wasn’t always this way. i was drastically different on a soul level even a month ago. ⁣
but allllll of the pain, all of the struggles, all of the questions...led me to this moment in time and i wouldn’t change a thing. ⁣
⁣
i wish this feeling of clarity for everyone and pray that everyone knows it’s possible. ⁣
it’s possible to live a life of peace, joy and harmony. ⁣
⁣
what is one thing you could do today to remove something in your life that doesn’t bring you joy at a soul level?!? ⁣
⁣
think on it. ⁣
⁣
✨🙏🏻💞⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣

not reacting to the humans that used to trigger me with their rudeness or negativity. ⁣
⁣
living 99.9999% of my days in a state of love now. ⁣
⁣
clearing out old baggage with ease and grace on the reg. ⁣
⁣
learning my soul’s purpose a little more each day and the excitement that comes with that. ⁣
⁣
having my mind blown daily with the amount of gratitude flowing through me. ⁣
⁣
the list of awesomeness could go on and on. ⁣
⁣
the life i’ve created and will continue to intentionally create is one of magical propoions. ⁣
⁣
life wasn’t always this way. i was drastically different on a soul level even a month ago. ⁣
but allllll of the pain, all of the struggles, all of the questions...led me to this moment in time and i wouldn’t change a thing. ⁣
⁣
i wish this feeling of clarity for everyone and pray that everyone knows it’s possible. ⁣
it’s possible to live a life of peace, joy and harmony. ⁣
⁣
what is one thing you could do today to remove something in your life that doesn’t bring you joy at a soul level?!? ⁣
⁣
think on it. ⁣
⁣
✨🙏🏻💞⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
                              ⁣⁣

r. kelly’s name has been tarnished with the recent release of lifetime’s documentary series, surviving r. kelly. while the singer received a lot of negative attention due to the horrific accusations made against him in the production’s testimonials, the singer has also received positive feedback in the form of streaming. et canada reports “a rep for spotify says streaming of the singer’s music has increased by 16 percent since the first part of the three-part docu-series aired on thursday.” many members of the public are confused about this rise, wondering why anyone would decide to listen to his music amid the resurfacing of horrendous accusations, including child pornography and molestation. jada pinkett smith took to twitter asking her fans if they could offer any insight into this issue: “so i got an article this morning about how r. kelly’s music sales and his streams have spiked substantially since the release of surviving r. kelly docuseries,” the actress said. “and i’m having a really difficult time understanding why. but i think it’s important to understand why.” this comes after spotify had back-peddled on their decision to remove r. kelly’s music from the platform’s playlist. when the fact that other accused still had their music under the streaming giant’s banner, the company decided to revert their radical decision.

listen, this is situation got me so vexed ⁣
i can’t stand a man with a god complex ⁣
child predator, woman beater, rapist⁣
all of the facts in your face can’t escape this ⁣
used to believe i could fly grade school mission ⁣
but now it’s time to take the key up outta the ignition ⁣
times up boy,you and beat the shot clock ⁣
if you support this man then you get blocked ⁣
you’d rather choose ignorance over innocence ⁣
i’m talking little black girls are you listening ⁣
black lives matter you protest the scene ⁣
but when i say “me too”, you think it’s time to make memes ⁣
black men, something just ain’t adding up ⁣
cuz yal should be the first one standing up ⁣
instead, yal lookin real real silent ⁣
when all that does is increase the violence ⁣
but no, not ever, it won’t be tolerated ⁣
could care less about the sales that he generated ⁣
the right side of history is where we all belong ⁣
my life is worth way more than a damn song. ⁣
⁣

💡. ⁣

as for any of my friends, followers, and anyone who sees this, please stand with these women against this horrible man ! unfollow him, delete his music, and mute r kelly!!!! #muterkelly #survivingrkelly #survivor #domesticviolence #sexualassault #awareness #standtogether #strength #hope #believesurvivors #metoo

text:
thank you speaker of the house nancy pelosi reception. san francisco, california 01.06.2019

congratulations speaker of the house nancy pelosi, icon of female power, reclaims role as speaker and seal place in history.

if you believe nothing else, please know you are worthy of unconditional love and acceptance - just as you are. ❤

pelosi statement on one year anniversary of supreme court ruling on marriage equality.

washington, d.c. – house democratic leader nancy pelosi today released this statement on the anniversary of the supreme court decision on marriage equality, which was announced on june 26, 2015: “this weekend, we mark one year since the supreme court unequivocally affirmed that equal justice means marriage equality.  in communities across america, loving lesbian, gay, bisexual and transgender americans are finally free to marry who they love and enjoy the same rights and privileges as other married couples.  with this monumental decision, america moved closer to fulfilling the promise of our greatest ideals. “one year later, however, lgbt americans are still targets of violence and a shameful agenda of discrimination advancing in statehouses and in the congress.  nearly two weeks after the heartbreaking anti-lgbt mass shooting that claimed the lives of 49 people and terrorized the lgbt community, congress must unite to disarm hate.  we must strive to end anti-lgbt discrimination everywhere by passing the equality act. “we rejoice at how far we have come together.  thanks to president obama, the stonewall inn is now a national monument.  in toppling ‘don’t ask, don’t tell’, passing inclusive hate crimes legislation, and winning marriage equality, we have the forward momentum needed to usher in a new era of progress for america.  let us continue to ensure equality for lgbt families, reject discrimination, and act to improve our country for all.” #madamspeaker #speakerpelosi #forthepeople #imwithher #nancypelosi

text:
#motivationalmonday

not too long ago my health was fading pretty fast... my life consisted of constant doctor visits and hospitals stays... on a good day i would take 19 pills ... on a bad day, i wouldn't be able to honestly tell you. it was pretty bad. i took what doctors told me and ran with it. every label they slapped on me, i wore. seemed like every lab work done came back with something new. pill after pill... treatment after treatment... and still i wasn't getting any better. i would spend my days in bed (tossing and turning because i wasn't able to sleep) and my nights throwing up medications non stop... got so bad that i named my toilet "booskie" ... i mean we spent all night cuddling, might as well name it. 
shit got pretty bad... my anxiety was off the charts... popping xanax on top of all my medications just so i could get some rest... which only made me irritable because sleep was something my body forgot how to do. i was hospitalized, had morphine pumping through my veins... and still no sleep. my body didn't know what to do with itself... i went 4 days of no sleep... by that 4th day ending it all was all i could think of. not because i hated life... but because i was tired of being tired.

then one day it happened...you can say i got mad... i cold turkey stopped all meds and treatments... i googled foods, vitamins, oils, and herbs i could use as an alternative. my primary of over a decade did not agree with my decision, and mailed me a letter letting me know they could no longer be my health care provider as i was going against their recommendations. i think getting that letter was the push i needed to take control of my life... i did just that... went to my local police station and dropped off all pills... i was doing this! ... the withdrawal stage was hell, to say the least... my body still feels the effects of all those pills.... especially my kidney and stomach. my journey has not been easy... and far from over... still dealing with health issues but i got this. there's no stopping me now... i've been enlightened!💜

text:
we are excited to celebrate this year’s first #featuredrosie @lynzylab ! thank you for sharing your #rosiestory with us!
.
.
it was the day after kavanaugh was sworn in, and i was sitting at home alone when i noticed my husband had forgotten to lock the door when he left for work that morning. i immediately got up to lock it, thinking to myself, “wow! anyone could have just walked in and tried to hurt me.” i didn’t agonize over the thought; it was just an impulse i had, and have had, many times before in similar situations. i was reminded of trump’s words about it being a scary time for the men in this country, and i chuckled at the irony. but that laughter soon turned to anger, and i began writing a song that, unbeknownst to me, would drastically change the course of my life.
.
i had no idea a scary time (for boys) would go viral when i posted it on social media that evening, but in three days’ time, the video racked up over 60 million views worldwide. the fact that it resonated with so many people in such a short time is a true testament to how many others felt exactly how i had been feeling in the wake of the ford-kavanaugh hearing, and long before that. of course, i have also received a ton of negative criticism from people who disagree with the song’s message, or who incorrectly assume i’m saying all men are bad. many also argue that women can do most of the things mentioned in the song, which is true. i do those things. but not without checking my surroundings. not without hearing my dad’s voice in my head, telling me to yell as loudly as i can if someone tries to rape me. not without holding my keys between my fingers to use as a weapon.
.
the bottom line is: if my husband had been home alone and noticed the door wasn’t locked, he would have locked it (maybe), and that would have been that. when i noticed, my first instinct was to lock it as soon as possible, and then feel instant relief that nothing terrible happened to me in the hours that it was unlocked. that’s what the song is about.
.

text:
popped out to #ateasesundays open mic in #chicago last night. this poem is called complicit to agreement. we have a dangerous culture of sexual abuse, sexual misconduct, and sexual inappropriateness. and social media has helped us to better identify who some of you really are. i'm thankful for the men and women who have been courageous enough to speak their truth. i'm thankful for the men and women who have chosen not to deflect, but rather try to understand. i'm thankful for the men and women who have publicly and privately identified themselves as part of the problem and are actively doing something about it. and lastly, i'm so thankful for the advocates and treatment teams that are available to support survivors in this retraumaitizing societal echo chamber of blame and shame. the sexual abuse hotline calls surged this weekend for a reason. please reach out to 1-800-656-hope (4673) if you need to talk with someone or receive local resources. further, if you know of or suspect that an adult is having a sexual relationship with a minor, please contact your local authorities and the national child abuse hotline at 1-800-25-abuse. even if the sexual contact happened in the past, please report it. reports can be made anonymously. 
thank you @jeronimo_speaks for capturing the moment.

箱根駅伝 ３位 東洋大学
・
・
・
往路 🏅優勝 👑
西山くん2年連続の区間賞
ほんとにスゴすぎるし嬉しかった！！
修二くん ラストラン🏃💨
めちゃめちゃかっこよくてかっこよくて
もう鉄紺のユニを着ている修二くんを
見るのがこれで最後なんだと思ったら
涙が止まらなかった。
酒井監督の区間配置は素晴しいと
改めて思った１日でした＼(^o^)／
・
・
・
復路  ３位🥉
目標にしていた優勝は出来なかったけど
最後まで諦めずに一生懸命な
粘りの走りはどの大学の選手よりも
東洋の選手がかっこよかった‪ʚ,,･ω･,,ɞ‬
・
・
・
修二くんの涙を見て自分も涙とまらなくて
本当にかっこいいなと思った😢
修二くんは優勝を経験したことが無くて
だから優勝してお兄ちゃんに追いつくって
そんな中、総合３位
きっと強くなるって信じてる🥺
駅伝好きになってから知ったから
応援できたのは３年間しかないけど
４年間お疲れ様でした！かっこよかった💗
・
・
・
東洋の報告会で
''渡邉奏太を起用出来なかった''って
言ってたのを一瞬たりとも聞き逃さなかった！
泣いた、ほんとに泣いた、、
きっと怪我で辛い思いをしたと思う。
今年は奏太くんは４年生
ラスト１年 トラックも駅伝も
全て満足のいく走りが出来ますように💭
奏太くんの笑顔が見れますように🤧
・
・
・
奏太くんは大学４年生 
あゆなは高校３年生
最後の学年だしきっと奏太くんも
頑張ってるはず！！！！！
だから、あゆなも頑張ろう(ง •̀_•́)ง
・
・
・
・

text:
i've watched the qspiracy since the beginning.

steve bannon left the wh august 2017 and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences? 'j-c' church militant, anyone?

abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit a hijacked party is just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt, with the goonsquad known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this and messes with the boombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on me me me bed. obviously someone has a lot to lose when none of the us intelligence agencies ends this loonatic travesty.

qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that goebbels would have died for. it is clear that stuff like pizzagate™ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still.

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are useless with the content - no way they are going to risk their business by taking responsibility.

there is no way that gop isn't aware of this - after all, cambridge analytica worked for ted cruz and john bolton. the whole narrative is built on the same facebook user data that bannon and the mercers reportedly got as cambridge analytica. pedofiles - i bet - but the way things are bundled sure makes goebbels shiver.

trump plays along with his tweets, gestures and words. the bigger issue still - the republicans willingly piggybacked this before the midterms and still keep abusing the faith of their fellow men.

this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

text:
kuvaan sen ulos -näyttely 9.–20.1.2019
.
kuvaan sen ulos -näyttely esittelee seksuaalista hyväksikäyttöä ja seksuaalista väkivaltaa kokeneiden teoksia. se on toteutettu yhteistyössä suomen trauma- ja dissosiaatioyhdistys disso ry:n ja suomen delfins ry:n kanssa. näyttelyyn osallistuu yhteensä 16 aikuista henkilöä, ja esillä on monin eri tekniikoin toteutettuja kuvia sekä veistoksia. lisäksi useat osallistujista ovat avanneet teoksiaan ja niiden tekoprosessia myös tekstin muodossa. näyttelytöitä alettiin kerätä keväällä 2018 osana #metoo-kampanjaa
.
lisätietoa näyttelystä: https://www.artkaarisilta.fi/21463

galleria art kaarisilta

00100 helsinki

however - while doing this djt, with the goonsquad known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this and messes with the boombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on me me me bed. obviously someone has a lot to lose when none of the us intelligence agencies ends this loonatic travesty.

qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that goebbels would have died for. it is clear that stuff like pizzagate™ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still.

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are useless with the content - no way they are going to risk their business by taking responsibility.

trump plays along with his tweets, gestures and words. the bigger issue still - the republicans willingly piggybacked this before the midterms and still keep abusing the faith of their fellow men.

this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

i've watched the qspiracy since the beginning.

steve bannon left the wh august 2017 and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences? 'j-c' church militant, anyone?

text:
did you know that oftentimes individuals don't even recognize they have experienced an abusive situation until long after it has occured? 🌱
in my experience as a therapist i can recall several encounters where abuse wasn't recognized until treatment began. this is why psychoeducation is a large component when helping individuals process trauma. 🌱
watching the rkelly documentary was unsettling. hearing some of the responses to the women sharing their stories was nauseating. there is a significant lack of understanding as it pertains to abuse in our community. 📣listen abuse is real and we must educate our communities on this topic.
i'm grateful that this series has created some conversation. however let's ensure that the conversations are healthy. as an observer educate yourself. become very curious about abuse and the mindset of the perpetrators and victims. instead of judging who you think is being dishonest stop and talk about what abuse is with you loved ones. explore your personal experiences with abuse. commit to seeking therapy.
🌱
it is my hope that this open platform will create more healthy conversations surrounding this topic. 🌱
be kind and gentle with one another yall! if you want to know more about the various types of abuse i'll post a link for resources on the spring forth counseling facebook page. feel free to like follow and share!

text:
come fanno le cellule del tumore a raggiungere organi distanti?

le cellule con capacità metastatiche che si moltiplicano nell'organo di origine riescono, con il tempo, a rompere le barriere del tessuto, fino a raggiungere i linfonodi più vicini, vere e proprie "stazioni di controllo" con il compito di bloccare il passaggio di molecole estranee o pericolose. se riescono a superare il filtro dei linfonodi, le cellule metastatiche si immettono nel circolo linfatico e possono raggiungere anche aree molto distanti dal loro tumore di origine.
dal circolo linfatico queste cellule possono anche passare in quello sanguigno, grazie alle numerose vie di comunicazione tra i due sistemi. 
a volte le cellule tumorali possono entrare direttamente nei vasi sanguigni attraversandone le pareti. se sopravvivono all'attacco del sistema immunitario, le cellule metastatiche possono raggiungere una nuova localizzazione dove riprodursi e dare origine a un nuovo tumore.
in altri casi le metastasi raggiungono l'organo bersaglio per sgocciolamento. ciò si verifica in cavità come l'addome. il peritoneo, per esempio, è la sottile membrana che riveste la cavità addominale e i visceri, ed è sede frequente di metastasi che provengono dall'ovaio, senza passare dai vasi sanguigni o linfatici.
#oncologia #breastcancerwarriors #tumorealseno #breastcancercare #metoo #europadonna #leguerrieresciencesartsandevents

text:
the price gap in switzerland, a case study. 
just like any other country, supermarkets in  switzerland also have a gender price gap. you just need to wonder around the daily use/sanitary use aisle to see the difference. a classic example is the cost of razors. in fact, in one of the most popular supermarkets in switzerland, coop the price of 8 bic lady razors is of 4.30 francs while a set of 10 razors for men is sold at 4.25 francs. this difference might not seem very big, however if you pay attention, there are 8 razors in the lady’s pack while there are 10 in the men’s one. after a glance at the two different razors, we can see that there is no major difference in their composition apart from their color which does not justify this price difference of 22%. i have been able to record the price difference between other articles like shampoos, shower gels or deodorants in the same supermarket and the difference is also noticeable. swipe to see in more detail the study conducted but also keep in mind that it was done with approximately 10 samples each time which while it allows us to see a clear tendency does not permit to have a totally accurate picture of the problem. . .
.
.
.

text:
head over to @princessbestspeaks. to watch full videos on igtv!

after watching carey kelly's radio interview where he revealed he and his brother r. kelly were molested by their older sister theresa, the universe wouldn't let me sleep until i addressed it. there are so many people from r. kelly to 3-4 generations back that need to be held accountable, and in order for sexual assault, sexual abuse, rape, molestation and abuse of power and control to be eradicated, we gotta heal this shit at the root. i'm in agreeance with #muterkelly music completely (bc stopping the way an abuser eats and survives helps bring struggle, reflection and perspective), but though it's hard, we can't mute the abuser we must push them to confront their denial for the violation they've caused and push them to be accountable and vocal about their sickness and don't let them off the hook by just writing them off. we can't stop violation of women & girls and others if we don't push for the abusers to speak up and not just the victims or all we do is create an insular talk. real talk we ain't solving shit with just victims and bystanders at the table. i could go on and on but check the latest podcast ( i had so much to say it's in 5 parts), click the igtv icon to watch!

topic: f*ck r. kelly & #metoo: how #blackgirlsmatter & abuse we create too (pt. 1-5)

after watching carey kelly's radio interview where he revealed he and his brother r. kelly were molested by their older sister theresa, the universe would not let me sleep until i addressed it. there are so many people from r. kelly to 3-4 generations back that need to be held accountable, and in order for sexual assault, sexual abuse, rape, molestation and abuse of power and control to be eradicated, we gotta heal this shit at the root. i am in agreeance with #muterkelly music completely (bc stopping the way an abuser eats and survives helps bring struggle, reflection and perspective), but though it is hard, we can not mute the abuser we must push them to confront their denial for the violation they've caused and push them to be accountable and vocal about their sickness and do not let them off the hook by just writing them off. we can not stop violation of women & girls and others if we do not push for the abusers to speak up and not just the victims or all we do is create an insular talk. real talk we ain't solving shit with just victims and bystanders at the table. i could go on and on but check the latest podcast ( i had so much to say it is in 5 parts), click the igtv icon to watch!

text:
tw: sexual assault, abuse

to the boy who dumped me for being assaulted the first time only to be the last person who assaulted me. if you hadn’t dumped me for the first time, i wouldn’t ever have met the man who would continuously assault me for 6 months. i have forgiven myself for falling for you the first time. i have forgiven myself for trying to fall for you the second time. i will never forgive you for being the manipulative, abusive monster that you are. 
though the sting of memories stands as a reminder, the wounds from you are healed. in 2019, i am finished dealing with the trauma you dealt me both in 2010 and 2015. i am focusing on the trauma in between and ridding my heart of any focus towards you or your “new” girlfriend who so desperately sucked me back in begging for help so many times. 
you are nothing but a rapist, a liar, a cheater, and an abuser. i have heard that fire cleanses things, even metaphorically from your heart and soul. with that being said, i hope you burn in hell 🔥

#sexualassault #metoo #timesup #rape #triggerwarning

text:
내가 정확히 알지 못하는 어떤 단어에 대해 특정한 느낌을 갖고 있다면 주체적 판단이 아니라 주입된 편견일 가능성이 높다. 내게 "페미니즘/페미니스트"는 그런 단어였다. 
우리가 겪었던 성차별/성폭력은 무수하며 여전하다. 나 또한 여성이 대다수인 공교육에 종사하는 초등교사이나 일부 관리자에 의한 성추행(술따르기, 손 주무르기, 함께 춤추기 강요, 기타 스킨쉽 등)을 당한 적이 았다. 몇년 전만에도 정말 불쾌하고 짜증나지만 관행처럼 참아내야 하는 줄 알았던 일이다. 
너무 놀라고 당황스러워 급히 연락했을때 오히려 그런 사실을 전한 내게 불쾌하고 화난다며 2차 가해를 했던 전 남친 a도 있었다. 다른 일상은 어떠한가. 운전이 서툴거나 주차를 잘못한 차를 보고 운전자를 확인하기도 전에 늘 "에휴 저 김여사, xx"라는 말을 달고 살아 결국 대판 싸웠던 b도 있었다. 제주도에 여성 피살 사건이 여러 번 있었을 때 "그러니까 자기도 앞으로 제주도 혼자 가지마"라고 말해 (그러니까, 피해자 잘못이라고??) 톡쏘는 면박을 받았던 남편도 있다. 
아파트 대단지 주변에 살면서 여전히 10시가 넘으면 산책로를 다니기가 두렵고, 엘리베이터에 마스크 쓴 남자라도 타면 늘 흠칫하며 돌발행동시 대처방안을 상상하는 내가 있다. '쌩얼'이나 나의 체형에 대해 자기비하를 하며 스스로를 성적대상화했던 나도 있다. 
똥통에서 태어나 살아가면 여기가 똥통인지, 아니면 세상이란 원래 이렇게 구수한건지 도통 알 도리가 없다. 유사이래 성차별과 성폭력이 만연한 여기/지구 위에서, "성에 의한 차별이 없는 공평한 세상"을 지향하고 노력해온 페미니즘을 (부끄럽지만,늦게나마) 지지한다. 무엇이 문제인지 알아야-말하고-행동할 수 있을 것이다. 
#남자들은자꾸나를가르치려든다 #리베카솔닛 #나도몰라서공부하는페미니즘 #키드작가 #페미니즘 #페미니스트 #metoo #독서일기 #책추천 #책리뷰 #취미 #일상 #책읽는이유 #무지해서

너무 놀라고 당황스러워 급히 연락했을때 오히려 그런 사실을 전한 내게 불쾌하고 화난다며 2차 가해를 했던 전 남친 a도 있었다. 다른 일상은 어떠한가. 운전이 서툴거나 주차를 잘못한 차를 보고 운전자를 확인하기도 전에 늘 "에휴 저 김여사, xx"라는 말을 달고 살아 결국 대판 싸웠던 b도 있었다. 제주도에 여성 피살 사건이 여러 번 있었을 때 "그러니까 자기도 앞으로 제주도 혼자 가지마"라고 말해 (그러니까, 피해자 잘못이라고??) 톡쏘는 면박을 받았던 남편도 있다. 
아파트 대단지 주변에 살면서 여전히 10시가 넘으면 산책로를 다니기가 두렵고, 엘리베이터에 마스크 쓴 남자라도 타면 늘 흠칫하며 돌발행동시 대처방안을 상상하는 내가 있다. '쌩얼'이나 나의 체형에 대해 자기비하를 하며 스스로를 성적대상화했던 나도 있다. 
똥통에서 태어나 살아가면 여기가 똥통인지, 아니면 세상이란 원래 이렇게 구수한건지 도통 알 도리가 없다. 유사이래 성차별과 성폭력이 만연한 여기/지구 위에서, "성에 의한 차별이 없는 공평한 세상"을 지향하고 노력해온 페미니즘을 (부끄럽지만,늦게나마) 지지한다. 무엇이 문제인지 알아야-말하고-행동할 수 있을 것이다. 
#남자들은자꾸나를가르치려든다 #리베카솔닛 #나도몰라서공부하는페미니즘 #키드작가 #페미니즘 #페미니스트 #metoo #독서일기 #책추천 #책리뷰 #취미 #일상 #책읽는이유 #무지해서

text:
as a woman survivor of childhood sexual abuse, this is a cause very close to my heart.  the damage sexual abuse has on our mental and emotional development is catastrophic.  childhood sexual abuse is one of the most well hidden crimes in this world, and this needs to change. 
the scary fact is that more than 8 out of 10 children who are sexually abused know their abuser!!! know them!! and trust them!!!. family, friends, neighbours, babysitters, teachers, parents!. many of them are well respected members of their communities... what is even scarier is that 1 out of 5 children are being sexually abused right now!  1 out of 5.  so next time you goto your childs school or have a birthday party remember these figures. 
it is so easy to sweep this epademic under the carpet!  but it needs to be spoken about more, these carpets need to be lifted... and all the dirt exposed under them and cleaned up!!! these are our children, our childrens children.  it is time for us to stand and to protect!!! the more aware we are the more we can keep our children safe.  i am not saying to wrap them up in cotton wool and not let them near anyone.  what i am saying is it is time to start having conversations around what is ok and what is not.  to start having conversations with each other... the more we talk and lift those carpets... the more we stand together as a tribe.... the more we stand strong.  the less room we give predators  to move in on our innocent.

sending love always xoxoxo 
share and like our page to spread awareness and start the conversation. <3 
#standup #metoo  #riseup 
head to the below link parents protect a great site of faq
be prepared.... https://www.parentsprotect.co.uk/faqs.htm#what%20is%20csa

if anyone you know is being abused right now call emergency services for your country immediately.

in australia 
emergency services 000

1800 respect
kids helpline 1800 859 284

if you are unsure of numbers to call in your countries or areas please pm me and i will help you find them.

text:
.
nu får det vara nog!
.
det jag gör, det gör jag för att jag vill ge alla en chans till en fin och trygg förlossning. det sker på olika sätt för alla och därför har jag också valt att jobba med er en-till-en, på ett väldigt personligt plan.
.
för ofta möter jag patienter och klienter som tidigare träffat en #doula
eller som gått en #profylaxkurs eller annan förberedande kurs och nu känner sig lurade och besvikna över att deras förlossning inte alls blev som de tänkt.

for the record, eftersom jag vet att det här kommer väcka starka reaktioner, vill jag säga: många doulor är helt underbara och deras jobb behövs och är viktigt. många idéer och tekniker fungerar bra och fint för många par. det är ju toppen när det gör det.
.
men... nu har jag fått så jäkla mycket nog av rent dumma råd och framförallt avrådanden kring förlossningar som vissa doulor och kursledare ger ut. . 
kvinnor föder olika. det finns igen mall! det finns inga vetenskapliga belägg för allt ni påstår kommer störa "en normal" förlossning, det finns inga "stressade bäcken" och alla förlossningar är "naturliga"!!!
. 
alla kvinnor kan omöjligt ha ett "rätt sätt" att föda på. det gör mig så ledsen och arg när jag ser de här kvinnorna som är livrädda för att de gör "fel" bara för att de blivit skammade inför förlossningen.
.
att staka ut endast en väg att ta sig till ett mål är att totalt beröva en person på en underbar upptäcktsfärd, om ni frågar mig. det borde förbjudas!
. 
det här året, för mig, kommer att handla om att avliva myter och ta tillbaka tilliten till vården igen.
. 
barnmorskor har studerat och arbetat många år, och undersköterskor har som regel lång erfarenhet inom just förlossningsvård, och de tillsammans bildar kompetens som ingen annan har tillgång till. det behöver ni kunna känna tillit till.
.
nu sätter jag stopp för halvsanningar och en massa mumbojumbo och jag tänker lägga i en högre växel för att nå mitt mål om din personliga trygghet när du ska bli förälder. för att jag vill så hjärtans gärna att det ska bli bra för er. 
sköt om er!
❤️
/lotta
name: Lotta Höckert

text:
finished watching the #rkelly documentary and i am in utter disgust. ladies please speak out! you are never alone and can be protected if you seek help! it is not your fault and you are not weak. i know so many women, including myself that have been victims to any form of abuse. do not be ashamed of judgement, denial or abandonment. you will be loved, accepted and most importantly rescued. you just have to be willing to rescue yourself to invite that assistance. i understand the profound agony that is experienced during an abusive relationship. the abuse only gets worse and continues to manifest when you remain silent!  you are loved! 🖤
.
.
.

text:
interrupting your perfectly curated timeline with some imperfect realness
...
growing three babies is no joke and i remind myself of that. so why carry on hating on my body when i am sincerely grateful for it! this is my vehicle and i choose to love and nourish it both inside and out.
...
the past six months for me has been a period of transformation. getting over self-sabotaging behaviors, negative internal and external dialogue, healing from childhood stuff and accepting myself fully...lumps, bumps and all! ...
take a minute to love the skin you’re in. know that you have the power to heal yourself and love yourself and fill your timeline with people and posts that inspire you. stop comparing...it is valuable time wasted. when those negative thoughts pop up...acknowledge them, but do not define yourself by them. you can choose the thoughts you think with awareness and conscious effort
...
lotsalovelissa
.
.
.
.
.

text:
今日在香港，拖喼，是一種很敏感的行為。

拖喼要型，首先要人憑喼 upgrade，然後，個人同個喼，一齊升呢。

唔係叫你一拖喼就好似占士邦返總部接受最新任務 briefing，但至少其人其 package，都能令人覺得，你隻喼裏面，裝着的是一半英文書，另一半係一隻意大利的木琴曼陀羅，而不是奶粉廁所板。

人要減肥，喼要減磅，精神要減壓，負荷要減辛。

做人已經太沉重，男性 executive 出 business trip ，據說因為怕 #metoo，不敢再同一個秀麗的新女秘書一齊出門。但拖一隻新秀麗 @samsonite_hk ，輕巧硬淨，的骰堅抽，入到間房，一手抱起，就掟落床，跟住拉開拉鍊，即伸手摷嘢，旅途就寂寞極都有限啦。

想睇真啲有幾輕巧硬淨？即入：http://bit.ly/2gqkdlv

#陶傑 #chiptso
#拖喼
#又要飛了

text:
after watching carey kelly's radio interview where he revealed he and his brother r. kelly were molested by their older sister theresa, the universe wouldn't let me sleep until i addressed it. there are so many people from r. kelky to 3-4 generations back that need to be held accountable, and in order for sexual assault, sexual abuse, rape, molestation and abuse of power and control to be eradicated, we gotta heal this shit at the root. i'm in agreeance with #muterkelly music completely (bc stopping the way an abuser eats and survives helps bring struggle, reflection and perspective), but though it's hard, we can't mute the abuser we must push them to confront their denial for the violation they've caused and push them to be accountable and vocal about their sickness and don't let them off the hook by just writing them off. we can't stop violation of women & girls and others if we don't push for the abusers to speak up and not just the victims or all we do is create an insular talk. real talk we ain't solving shit with just victims and bystanders at the table. i could go on and on but check the latest podcast ( i had so much to say it's in 5 parts), click the igtv icon to watch!

text:
the girl who never kept her mouth shut?
have you ever been infatuated by strong, badass, female characters.
be it blair waldorf running down a bunch of teenage girls at the steps of the met, be it samantha jones using men at a pace faster than the city traffic, be it cordelia goode burning men at stakes, be it cersei lannister bombing an entire monument while sipping on dornish wine or be it miranda priestley running the fashion industry like a queen.
a few of these  characters were dark and murderous, don’t go that far, but there’s a little to learn from all these lovely empowered characters, beauty is power, it has caused wars and battles, using beauty to our advantage is not objectifying ourselves but it’s simply using something that we have to make a better living, beauty mixed with a little bit of brain, a pinch of manipulation, a dash of skin show, and loads of knowledge and creativity can take you anywhere.
so it’s okay to let loose of morals if you’re getting something better, life is about weighing your options and then choosing them, what you do to chose them is upto you, your choice, your call, your right.
it’s better to use them than getting used by them, so ladies, bring out your inner bitches and don’t be afraid of anyone, because we’re all worth it, in fact, better than it.

text:
bannon wanted to use the sorts of aggressive messaging tactics usually reserved for geopolitical conflicts to move the us electorate further to the right, wylie said. he had already directed a series of anti-establishment, conservative documentary films and presided over the far-right website breitbart news, but cambridge analytica would mark another step in his overall ambitions to transform the nation.

with financial backing from hedge-fund billionaire robert mercer, bannon co-founded cambridge analytica in 2013 as the us-branch of strategic communication laboratories (scl) group, a british company that advertises how it has conducted "behavioral change" programs in more than 60 countries.

wylie described cambridge analytica as - steve bannon and robert mercer using a foreign, military contractor ... to use some of the same techniques that the military uses ... on the american electorate.

curt devine, donie o'sullivan and drew griffin
cnn

text:
wylie said that bannon's plans began to solidify in 2014, when cambridge analytica consulted various republican campaigns and pacs ahead of the midterm elections. the company began to test and apply its psychographics by using facebook data to model individuals' personality types in order to understand how to influence them.

documents show the john bolton super pac, which promoted candidates supported by recently appointed white house national security adviser john bolton, paid cambridge analytical $454,700 in 2014 for "behavioral microtargeting with psychographic messaging." those services included strategies that broke individual voters into "clusters" based on what messages would resonate with them.

wylie also said the company used focus groups and messaging trials in 2014 to test some of the concepts that became core themes of the trump campaign, such as "drain the swamp" and imagery of walls. "a lot of the narratives of the trump campaign were what we were testing in 2014," wylie said.

he added that bannon directly presided over much of the company's initial research. "everything that we were doing ultimately had to be passed up to bannon for approval," said wylie, who left the company in late 2014.

wylie said bannon would fly to london about once a month for company meetings, and during that time he came to understand bannon's ideology. "he really liked the idea of using a military-style approach to changing people's perceptions," wylie said.

curt devine, donie o'sullivan & drew griffin
cnn

text:
@infoscreening -  under the spirit of #metoo, we highlighted the case of sexual violence that is still prevalent in today's society, particularly towards girls and women. with that in mind, almost unanimously, we understood the importance of consent in sexual activities.

but, is consent enough? in 2018 we saw worrying trend of misusing the concept of consent in dealing with sexual violence cases. almost exactly one year ago, we witnessed the entire aziz ansari fiasco with an anonymous woman's account accusing him of sexual violence. in ansari's defense, the act had been consensual. late 2018, irish feminists went enraged as a rape victim's underwear was produced in court as a proof that she'd consented to the harm done to her. of course, we haven't even delved further into the case of agni from ugm and the fact that there are still people who believe that she somewhat must have wanted it.

it is timely that now we have an open discussion about what consent is and more importantly, what it is not. surely, it is not a justification for rape. let's discuss further in our event below:

topic: beyond consent

venue: @kenobispace — gedung colony kemang, lt. 6

schedule:

18.45 - 20.15: movie screening

ticket: 30k

warning: the film is rated r and includes some rape and gore scenes.

discussion will be held in bahasa indonesia.

text:
wylie said that bannon's plans began to solidify in 2014, when cambridge analytica consulted various republican campaigns and pacs ahead of the midterm elections. the company began to test and apply its psychographics by using facebook data to model individuals' personality types in order to understand how to influence them.

documents show the john bolton super pac, which promoted candidates supported by recently appointed white house national security adviser john bolton, paid cambridge analytical $454,700 in 2014 for "behavioral microtargeting with psychographic messaging." those services included strategies that broke individual voters into "clusters" based on what messages would resonate with them.

wylie also said the company used focus groups and messaging trials in 2014 to test some of the concepts that became core themes of the trump campaign, such as "drain the swamp" and imagery of walls. "a lot of the narratives of the trump campaign were what we were testing in 2014," wylie said.

he added that bannon directly presided over much of the company's initial research. "everything that we were doing ultimately had to be passed up to bannon for approval," said wylie, who left the company in late 2014.

wylie said bannon would fly to london about once a month for company meetings, and during that time he came to understand bannon's ideology. "he really liked the idea of using a military-style approach to changing people's perceptions," wylie said.

text:
in his first post-white house interviews, steve bannon, the rightwing ideologue who helped propel donald trump to the white house, made clear that he had no intention of going quietly. - i’ve got my hands back on my weapons, the former white house chief strategist, who returned as executive chairman of breitbart news late friday afternoon, told the weekly standard. - i built a f***ing machine at breitbart. and now i’m about to go back, knowing what i know, and we’re about to rev that machine up. and rev it up we will do.

just hours after his departure from the trump administration became public, breitbart, whose traffic and advertising have fallen significantly since trump’s election, trumpeted the return of their “populist hero” on its homepage. - the populist-nationalist movement got a lot stronger today, breitbart editor-in-chief alex marlow said in the publication’s announcement post. - breitbart gained an executive chairman with his finger on the pulse of the trump agenda.

the fall of steve bannon is a win for the globalists. but will it last?

also on friday, the once-again head of breitbart told bloomberg news: - if there’s any confusion out there, let me clear it up: i’m leaving the white house and going to war for trump against his opponents – on capitol hill, in the media, and in corporate america.

the 63-year-old also retains the backing of hedge-fund billionaire robert mercer. the pair met on wednesday to plot their future plans, bloomberg reported.

julia carrie wong
the guardian

black women & girls fucking matter. period't.

text:
u.s. president donald trump's former aide steve bannon sought to use personal information collected online to promote "a culture war," a whistleblower on now-defunct political data firm cambridge analytica told u.s. senators on wednesday.

bannon, a former cambridge analytica vice president, "saw cultural warfare as a means to create enduring change in american politics," testified christopher wylie, who says information about tens of millions of facebook users ended up in cambridge analytica's hands.

bannon's attorney william burck did not immediately respond to an email request for comment on wylie's testimony.

wylie, who worked for scl, the british-based parent of cambridge analytica, told the senate judiciary committee that cambridge analytica hired hackers to collect data it then used against opponents of its political clients.

allegations of the improper use of data for 87 million facebook users by cambridge analytica, which was hired by trump's 2016 election campaign, have led to investigations in the united states and europe.

mark hosenball
reuters

text:
🖤 “i am going to use my platform to say right now that in two years, everything that i produce and i am making a vow and it’s going to be tough to make sure that everything that i produce, that it’s fifty percent women.
i challenge anyone out there who is in a position of power, not just in or industry, in all industries, i challenge you to challenge yourselves and stand with us in solidarity and do the same.” yes @iamreginaking 🖤
💪🏿and also yes! to the sensational sandra oh on becoming the first asian woman in 40 years to win in the tv drama category! 💪🏿
2018 saw the launch of the @timesupnow movement, we watched dr. christine blasey ford amongst hundreds of other survivors speak out in alignment with the #metoo movement, we watched @ginamartinuk enforce a new law that upskirting is now illegal, we watched 82 women stand in solidarity to acknowledge the lack of female filmmakers throughout the history of the cannes film festival... all of these, amongst a million other successes/battles... what a bloody year. i’m pretty excited to see what we do next. 
#5050by2020

text: la parità di presenza delle donne nel cinema, il valore della diversità, i diritti dei migranti, degli omosessuali, la lotta al razzismo nei confronti degli afroamericani. i golden globe 2019, un anno dopo la prima premiazione dell'era del #metoo (ricordate gli abiti neri e i discorsi dal palco?), si sono svolti all'insegna dell'inclusione e della diversità. sul palco del beverly hills hotel sono saliti talenti che rappresentano la complessità della società in un'edizione dei premi della foreign press (i giornalisti stranieri a hollywood) che quest'anno ha abbracciato quanto mai il cinema black e con la scelta di una dei due conduttori della serata, l'attrice canadese di origine coreana sandra oh, con il comico adam samberg, a rappresentare la comunità asiatica dopo il successo del film crazy rich asians #glodenglobe #goldenglobes2019 #goldenglobes seguici su @larepubblica: il mondo in diretta anche su instagram

text:
former u.s. national security adviser michael flynn admitted on friday that he asked russia to delay a u.n. vote seen as damaging to israel, but diplomats said it was not the only country he and presidential adviser jared kushner lobbied.

in the hours before the vote by the 15-member united nations security council on dec. 23, flynn also phoned the u.n. missions of uruguay and malaysia, and kushner spoke with kim darroch, the british ambassador to the united states, according to diplomats familiar with the conversations, who spoke on condition of anonymity.

the lobbying took place before republican president donald trump, who was known for his pro-israel campaign rhetoric, took office on jan. 20. it failed, with the security council adopting a resolution demanding an end to israeli settlement building on land palestinians want for an independent state. the vote was 14 in favor and one abstention by the united states.

the efforts made on israel's behalf capped several days of unusual diplomacy. in a surprise dec. 21 move, egypt had called for a vote the next day on the draft resolution, prompting both trump and israel to urge washington to veto the text.

a senior israeli official told reuters that israeli officials contacted trump's transition team at a "high level" to ask for help after failing to persuade democratic president barack obama's administration to veto the draft u.n. resolution.

according to court documents made public on friday, a member of trump's presidential transition team, later identified by sources as trump's son-in-law kushner, told flynn on dec. 22 to contact officials from foreign governments, including russia, to convince them to delay the vote or veto the resolution.

flynn spoke with then-russian ambassador to the united states sergei kislyak that day, and again the following day, according to the court documents.

michelle nichols
reuters

text:
sexual molestation.. (pt 1)
mjue mbakaji
.
.
swala la r. kelly ni pana sana. 
wahusika…
a. mbakaji
b. mbakwaji
c. mzazi/mlezi
.
.
mjue mbakaji
mbakaji/anaewafanya watoto wadogo mapenzi [molestor] ni mtu wa karibu, anaaminiwa, mcheshi, na ni mtu wa watu.

1/3 ya molestors wanaundugu na mtoto na wengi ni wanaume. molestor anatumia mbinu mbalimbali za kumshawishi mtoto kwa muda mrefu na kumfikisha mahali huyu mtoto anamwamini [grooming] – mfano anamnunulia vitu anavyovipenda – inategemea na umri wa mtoto [pipi, simu, trip za nje]. kumbuka anakuwa amepania/amua kulala na huyu mtoto, kwahio anamsoma na kumjua ni vitu gani atavipenda na atavitumia kumdanganya. mtoto atakubali kufanya mapenzi shauri ananunuliwa vitu au na kushindwa kukataa shauri tayari ameishavikubali vitu ambavyo huyu mtu anatumia kama deni.
.
.
wengine wanatafuta urafiki na wazazi, ili waweze kuingia kwenye maisha ya watoto.
.

au mbakaji, anamtishia mtoto asiseme na akisema atamfanyia vitu vibaya na ataendelea kumbaka kwa kipindi kirefu bila watu kujua shauri atakuwa anaongopa kusema.
.

mbakaji anaweza kuwa baba, baba wa kambo, mjomba, rafiki wa kiume wa baba, wahusika kwenye nyumba za ibada, walimu shuleni, marafiki, dreva, dada au kaka wa kazi nyumbani.
.

pia mtu mwenye pesa ambaye akipelekwa mahakamani atashinda kesi kwa kuhonga.
.

r. kelly aliwabaka wengi kwa muda mrefu kwa kuwa alikua ni mtu maarafu na alitumia pesa kuwadanganya wasichana. nadhani hata hapa tanzania kuna msanii mmoja alilaumiwa na watu kuwa na mapenzi na mtoto mdogo shauri alikuwa anapesa na alitumia usanii kama chambo cha kumwingiza kwenye hayo maisha.
.
molester anawinda mtoto mwenye aibu, mahitaji [vulnerable, needy], walioshindikana, kwani wanahitaji sana marafiki na upendo. hawa watoto watakubali chochote na watatunza siri haswa wakiwa wanahongwa au kutishiwa.
.

mtoto [wakike na wakiume] anazungukwa na watu wa aina mbalimbali kama r.kelly na wanakuja kwa njia mbalimbali. je tunaweza kumtambua molestor?
.
.
